These are Puzzles for 3x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-1::.
The people grow 7 different varities of flowers: orchid, lily, tulip, balloon-flower, poppy, dahlia, iris
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: blues, classical, jazz, r&b, reggae, rock, soul
There are 7 different favourite colors: red, lilac, coral, azure, orange, green, ivory
 1. the person who growspoppy is on the far left##1
 2. the person who likes lilac is on the left of the person who growsorchid##1
 3. the person who likes ivory is between the fan of classical and the fan of blues##2
 4. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left of the person who likes green##1
 5. the fan of classical is on the left of the person who growslily##1
 6. the person who growsorchid is the person who likes ivory##1
 7. the fan of r&b is between the person who likes azure and the person who growspoppy##2
 8. the person who likes orange is on the left of the person who likes green##1
 9. the person who likes green is on the left of the person who likes red##1
10. the person who growsiris is the fan of jazz##1
11. the fan of rock is the person who growsballoon-flower##1
12. the person who growsiris is on the left of the person who growstulip##1
13. the person who likes red is the fan of reggae##1
14. the person who growsdahlia is between the person who likes coral and the person who likes ivory##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3      |    4     |   5    |     6      |    7     |
| Flower   | poppy | orchid     | dahlia | lily | balloon-flower | iris  | tulip  |
| Music-Genre   | blues  | r&b        | classical  | soul     | rock   | jazz       | reggae   |
| Color         | lilac   | ivory | azure    | coral  | orange | green | red |

