.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-2::.
There are 7 different favourite colors: lilac, yellow, lavender, purple, blue, ebony, brown
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: badminton, cricket, handball, parkour, sailing, snowboarding, soccer
There are 7 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, iced-tea, cola, milk, coffee, fanta, juice
 1. the person who likes yellow is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
 2. the person who's sport is sailing is the person who's sport is sailing##1
 3. the person who's sport is sailing is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1
 4. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 5. the person who's sport is badminton is the person who likes brown##1
 6. the person who likes lilac is the person drinking milk##1
 7. the person who likes lilac is between the person who's sport is soccer and the person drinking juice##2
 8. the person who's sport is handball is on the left of the person who likes blue##1
 9. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1
10. the person who likes lavender is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
11. the person who likes blue is on the right of the person who likes lilac##1
12. the person drinking almond-milk is the person who likes yellow##1
13. the person who likes purple is on the left of the person who likes lilac##1
14. the person who likes purple is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
15. the person who likes yellow is on the far right##1
16. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the person who likes brown##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3       |    4     |   5    |     6     |    7     |
| Color   | ebony | brown      | purple     | lilac  | blue | lavender | yellow |
| Sport         | cricket  | badminton | snowboarding | handball | soccer | parkour   | sailing  |
| Beverage     | cola   | fanta     | juice        | milk  | coffee   | iced-tea       | almond-milk      |

