10. the person who's sport is golf is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1
11. the person driving the roller is the person who's sport is skiing##1
12. the person who's sport is golf is on the right of the person watching satire movies##1
13. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1
