 3. the person drinking iced-tea is the person who growsazalea##1
 4. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the far right##1
 5. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person eating radish##1
 6. the person eating blueberry is on the far right##1
 7. the person eating apricot is in the middle##1
 8. the person who growsazalea is on the left of the person who growspoppy##1
 9. the person drinking water is the person who growsrose##1
10. the person drinking soy-milk is the person eating pumpkin##1
11. the person who growsbegonia is the person drinking lemonade##1
12. the person eating banana is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
13. the person drinking fanta is on the far right##1
14. the person who growsdaffodil is between the person who growsbegonia and the person who growsazalea##2
15. the person eating strawberry is on the right of the person who growspoppy##1

.:: Answer ::.
